<subSubSection id="C579540EABE553402647E2D5752B3D4A" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="D878FC04ADA87AF9A868F2E32D186F10" pageId="0" pageNumber="151">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B7BD48DD7B8C2E6B6AD71AD47EB0E862" pageId="0" pageNumber="151">
This species is dedicated to the Coreguaje community inhabiting along the piemont and lower parts of the 
<normalizedToken id="0EEAC58E489EF483948BC933F19B07C0" originalValue="Caquetá">Caqueta</normalizedToken>
River and its affluents.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="6453B2822C0FB87508803039E298899F" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="6BF032EC9A4227CC7A8C7386D0B993A6" pageId="0" pageNumber="151">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="755FFF16ED6CF424A78DF5E67AB956D2" pageId="0" pageNumber="151">Known only from the type locality.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
